       The user can run _r_._g_r_o_w either interactively or non-interactively.  The
       program  is run interactively if the user types rr..ggrrooww without specify-
       ing flag settings and parameter values on the command  line.   In  this
       case, the user will be prompted for input.


       Alternately,  the  user can run _r_._g_r_o_w non-interactively, by specifying
       the names of an iinnppuutt and oouuttppuutt map layer, and including  any  desired
       flags, on the command line.



